snippet.title: GearHead Caramel Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
GearHead Caramel is an upcoming turn based tactics style Roguelike mecha RPG. This is the third game in the GearHead series, and the first to be released on Steam. Animation by the incredible Matt Sandbrook.

http://www.gearheadrpg.com
